<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_3ed576d57a43.aspx"><b>周颂·噫嘻</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contson3ed576d57a43">
<p>噫嘻成王，既昭假尔。率时农夫，播厥百谷。骏发尔私，终三十里。亦服尔耕，十千维耦。</p>
